{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Be sure to <strong>WISHLIST</strong>\u00a0on Steam!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to <strong>Fat Goblins</strong>, where chaos, chubbiness, and class based combat come together in the form of 16v16 giant castle battles! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Prepare for goblin-packed, hat-stealing, and princess-fattening team based combat with up to 32 friends!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450350/extras/fat_goblins_mountain-horizontal-fly-over-1_cropped.mp4.gif?t=1733909830\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Don different hats to launch fireballs, heal teammates, shoot arrows, or just slice your way through the enemy team!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450350/extras/fat_goblins_ice-mage-combat-2_cropped.mp4.gif?t=1733909830\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Breach the walls and rescue your pudgy princess from the clutches of the enemy castle!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450350/extras/fat_goblins_break-down-doors_cropped.mp4.gif?t=1733909830\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fatten up your captive royal with delicious meat you scavenge from your teammates &amp; enemies corpses!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2450350/extras/fat_goblins_ambush-throw-1_cropped.mp4.gif?t=1733909830\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Win games to upgrade your runes and create the best hat!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragrap